======================================================================
KEY: Is h₂_rel correlated with β₁(T\v)?
======================================================================

  (h₂_rel, β₁(T\v)) cross-tabulation:
    h₂_rel=0, β₁=0: 2800
    h₂_rel=0, β₁=1: 1080
    h₂_rel=1, β₁=1: 600

  h₂_rel=0, β₁=0: 2800
  h₂_rel=0, β₁>0: 1080
  h₂_rel>0, β₁=0: 0
  h₂_rel>0, β₁>0: 600

  h₂_rel>0 IMPLIES β₁>0 (necessary but not sufficient)
  Equivalently: β₁=0 IMPLIES h₂_rel=0
  So: if T\v is acyclic (β₁=0), then h₂_rel=0 automatically!

